text:
Virtually all of the people on Farcaster with large audiences:

1. Don't have large audiences elsewhere (Farcaster is their first time with a large audience)

2. Didn't know me or Varun and didn't know each other. The "Farcaster OG scene" is net new creation of Farcaster.

3. Were early and stuck around when everyone made fun of Farcaster (and people still do)

4. Continued to cast interesting stuff, casted in channels when we suggested people cast in channels

5. Warpcast onboarding asks all users for their interests

6. Based on the interests, we pair the account with an initial set of follows

7. There are 200+ accounts on the list, weighted toward accounts that get the most engagement / drive retention, but a large group of people benefit

8. On our list to improve, but the reality is outside of "I should be on the list!" haven't seen any concrete proposals to improve

Guys we need your help! Brian is trapped at SEC Headquarters as we speak. Gary has him locked away in the interrogation room. 

Thankfully, a group of incredibly skilled hackers from a group called the /1337 Skulls were able to tap into the intercoms system at the SEC and give all of us the ability to communicate with Brian directly. Here's the catch: we can only command Brian to move using the four cardinal directions: N, E, S, W.

When asking Brian to move, go to the /brians-rescue channel and enter the command: 

!movebrian <dir>

If your command is correct, Brian gets one step closer to the exit. If any of you enter an incorrect command, Brian will be sent back to the start. 

Work together to help Brian escape Gary's evil clutches. But the last of you to enter the correct command wins the entire round. Good luck!

Hey Farcaster family, looking for your help and DEGEN tips! A family member has the chance to join a rare and relatively expensive volleyball club, and I'm raising funds to make it happen.

Here's how it works:

- Current $DEGEN price: ~half a cent
- For every legit tip I receive on this cast (or QC by me), I will match it 
- I'll donate matched amount at 1 full cent per DEGEN

Example:

- You tip 100 $DEGEN
- I match 100
